<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.1.10">
<l>kuṟuka mikavuṇar vattoṭu nōkkiyel lāmviṭṭa</l>
<l>iṟuka liṟappeṉṉu ñāṉikku mappaya ṉillaiyēl</l>
<l>ciṟuka niṉaivatōr pācamuṇ ṭāmpiṉṉum vīṭillai</l>
<l>maṟukali līcaṉaip paṟṟi viṭāviṭil vīṭaḵtē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even to a sage who is called the emancipation by contraction who has let go of all,</l>
<l>much looking at [it] with [his] consciousness so as to shrink, if that benefit is not there,</l>
<l>thinking in order to diminish will be one bond, and yet again there is no liberation.</l>
<l>If without letting go at all [you] grip the steady lord, that is liberation.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
